lead_paragraph: No. 20 Michigan State stunned No. 5 Ohio State in three overtimes, and the Buckeyes now need Maryland to lose to Minnesota in order to share the Big Ten crown.

abstract: College Basketball Women's Roundup; Michigan State defeats Ohio State, 107-105; other women's college basketball scores noted.
